{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":311181,"duration_api_ms":277005,"num_turns":36,"result":"Now output the required JSON:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"change_summary\": \"Extended TaskRunEntry with run_id, plan_hash, and outcome_detail fields. Added update_task_run and find_runs_for_bead methods to TaskRunLineagePort trait with FS adapter implementation. Updated record_bead_start and record_bead_completion signatures to accept and pass through the new fields. All new fields are Option<String> with serde defaults for backward compatibility with existing NDJSON data.\",\n  \"steps\": [\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Extended TaskRunEntry in model.rs with three new optional fields: run_id, plan_hash, outcome_detail — all with #[serde(default, skip_serializing_if)] for backward compatibility\",\n      \"order\": 1,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added update_task_run method to TaskRunLineagePort trait in service.rs — updates most recent matching entry by bead_id + project_id, setting outcome, outcome_detail, and finished_at\",\n      \"order\": 2,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added find_runs_for_bead method to TaskRunLineagePort trait in service.rs — filters task runs by bead_id returning all attempts in chronological order\",\n      \"order\": 3,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Implemented update_task_run in FsTaskRunLineageStore (fs.rs) — reads all entries, finds last match by bead_id+project_id, updates it, rewrites file atomically\",\n      \"order\": 4,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Implemented find_runs_for_bead in FsTaskRunLineageStore (fs.rs) — delegates to read_task_runs and filters by bead_id\",\n      \"order\": 5,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Updated record_bead_start signature to accept run_id: Option<&str> and plan_hash: Option<&str>, passing them through to TaskRunEntry construction\",\n      \"order\": 6,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Updated record_bead_completion signature to accept run_id: Option<&str>, plan_hash: Option<&str>, and outcome_detail: Option<&str>, passing them through to TaskRunEntry construction\",\n      \"order\": 7,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added service-level find_runs_for_bead and update_task_run wrapper functions for clean API access\",\n      \"order\": 8,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added test: task_run_entry_serialization_with_new_fields — verifies round-trip JSON serialization of all new fields\",\n      \"order\": 9,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added test: task_run_entry_backward_compat_without_new_fields — verifies old-format JSON without new fields deserializes correctly with None defaults\",\n      \"order\": 10,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added test: find_runs_for_bead_filters_correctly — verifies filtering returns only matching bead entries across multiple beads and retries\",\n      \"order\": 11,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added test: update_task_run_modifies_outcome — verifies in-place update of a Running entry to Succeeded with outcome_detail and finished_at\",\n      \"order\": 12,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added test: multiple_retries_visible_for_same_bead — verifies two attempts (fail then succeed) for the same bead are all visible with correct plan_hash and outcome values\",\n      \"order\": 13,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Updated existing bead_start_and_completion_tracking test to exercise new fields (run_id, plan_hash, outcome_detail) and verify they persist correctly\",\n      \"order\": 14,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"validation_evidence\": [\n    \"All 60 milestone_record tests pass: cargo test --lib contexts::milestone_record (60 passed; 0 failed)\",\n    \"cargo clippy -- -D warnings passes with zero warnings\",\n    \"cargo fmt --check passes with no formatting issues\",\n    \"Backward compatibility test confirms old-format NDJSON without new fields deserializes correctly (run_id, plan_hash, outcome_detail all default to None)\",\n    \"find_runs_for_bead correctly returns 4 entries for bead-1 (2 attempts × start+complete), 2 for bead-2, and 0 for non-existent bead\",\n    \"update_task_run correctly modifies the most recent matching entry in-place and rewrites the NDJSON file atomically\"\n  ],\n  \"outstanding_risks\": [\n    \"update_task_run rewrites the entire task-runs.ndjson file atomically — for milestones with very large lineage files this could be slow, but is acceptable for current scale\",\n    \"No callers outside tests currently pass the new fields — controller integration (bead 8.1) will need to supply run_id, plan_hash, and outcome_detail when calling record_bead_start/record_bead_completion\"\n  ]\n}\n```","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"428ca158-079f-4a0d-90d8-49375a1c0644","total_cost_usd":1.79362565,"usage":{"input_tokens":35,"cache_creation_input_tokens":60162,"cache_read_input_tokens":1908792,"output_tokens":13897,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":60162,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":35,"outputTokens":13897,"cacheReadInputTokens":1908792,"cacheCreationInputTokens":60162,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":1.6780084999999998,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":64000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":227,"outputTokens":4777,"cacheReadInputTokens":275614,"ca